title: Ranked Queue Downtime
body:
Did they start disabling ranked queues at 4 again? 
on monday morning ranked was running all day now it get disabled at 4 and im confused

replies.body:
Hi,

It is still meant to be disabled from 4am - 8am AEST each day.  On Monday we had an issue with our scheduling process that turns on & off the queue, which resulted in Ranked staying on accidentally.

Cheers
Mindstar
